**Assign serial / lot number to Item**

Firstly you need to assign a serial and a lot number to an Item, for example the item 1896-S "Scrivania Atene". Open the Item card and fill in the fields in the tab "Item Tracking":

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000103-0/1InvSerLot.png"><br>

**Item Journal - Posting**

Let's see an example of posting.

Open the page Item Journals and enter a new line:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000103-0/2InvSerLot.png"><br>

From Line->Item Tracking Lines set the Serial / Lot Number and the Quantity as shown:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000103-0/3InvSerLot.png"><br>

Now we can post the lines on the Item Journals page:

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000103-0/4InvSerLot.png"><br>